text: @RandPaul How many people who are asymptomatic have #Coronavirus but we don’t know because they can’t get tested like a Senator can? Will you return to your 2016 self & criticize @realDonaldTrump for ignoring warnings https://t.co/ZswqvZA2oW & not testing & preparing? Or remain his buddy?
